QuestData.Title: Urgent Delivery
QuestData.RewardText: Are you $n? It's about time! I'd just about given up on finding you!$B$BThere's an urgent message waiting for you at the mailbox. The person that gave it to me was a human admiral from Azuremyst. Admiral Odesy-something... the name escapes me. He said you would know who he was.$B$B<Hermesius shrugs.>
